@table @asis
@item @b{Syntax:}
result = @b{it}(<@i{pos}| @{@i{x}, @i{y}@}|@i{x}, @i{y}| @i{obj} | @i{group}| @i{polist}>)

@item @b{Details:}
If the argument describes a single position, the item object at this position
