@node usertype
@subsection usertype
@findex usertype

The function @samp{usertype()} returns type info for Enigma data types.

@table @asis
@item @b{Syntax:}
@b{usertype}(@i{var})

@table @asis
@item @i{var}
Any kind of variable.
@end table

@item @b{Syntax Samples:}
@example
@var{argtype} = @i{usertype}(@var{value})
@end example

